{"tid":2305451,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"12港人送中滿百日 市民登望夫石舉「SAVE 12」燈牌","createTime":"2020-11-29T15:45:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-30T01:21:37.000Z","uid":126797,"like":89,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"61ffc507a391b06dfcdf9950b956082709640db1","tid":2305451,"uid":126797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T15:45:04.000Z","msg":"12港人遭中國當局扣押在深圳鹽田看守所，至明日（11月30日）便滿100日。繼10月3日有熱心市民登上獅子山頂，舉起「SAVE 12」燈牌後，今日晚上他們再攀上望夫石，以同一方式表達思念之餘，亦呼籲市民毋忘送中12港人。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WgtruhM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWgtruhM.png&h=dd24ea78&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ps2f64v.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fps2f64v.png&h=f90e109f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20201129/2QSGZ44YZ5HRTL7Z5W57GYDLTY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20201129%2F2QSGZ44YZ5HRTL7Z5W57GYDLTY%2F&d=73P4J9mxZbud55ZbF8SGiXO0ZW31AiaZ%2BXmqixBX3cM%3D&h=93df6fd9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20201129%2F2QSGZ44YZ5HRTL7Z5W57GYDLTY%2F&h=3a4af325\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20201129/2QSGZ44YZ5HRTL7Z5W57GYDLTY/</a>"},{"pid":"4f18ae84bd87e6e6ae0a5c00cf5fb98c8503fc78","tid":2305451,"uid":126797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T15:46:35.000Z","msg":"自推10連<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7cb4356ae7f580443aef7e9721b300baba4db9a","tid":2305451,"uid":126797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T15:46:49.000Z","msg":"9<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e942848b28d5a3a48859519df7981777295d4c7","tid":2305451,"uid":126797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T15:47:01.0